  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to see what a lab test will show and if there is a way to
      predict which patients will be more likely to have rejection after receiving a liver
      transplant.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is simply to see what the new oligonucleotide microarrays will show
      when comparing the the different patient groups. The results of this study will be one of the
      first steps In exploring the potential use of this new test.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
